00:52:09.300 --> 00:52:13.950
my life over the past five years is "Happiness
Hypothesis." The author looks at a whole bunch

00:52:13.950 --> 00:52:20.631
of different religions, philosophers and,
and, and, and religions, philosophers and

00:52:20.631 --> 00:52:25.090
cultures from different time periods, and
